articles.author: Daniel Kreps
articles.title: See Dua Lipa Bring Out Tame Impala's Kevin Parker at Glastonbury - Rolling Stone
articles.description: Dua Lipa headlined the Glastonbury Festival on Friday night, and during her set she brought out Tame Impala’s Kevin Parker to join her on two tracks.
articles.content:
Dua Lipa headlined the Glastonbury Festival on Friday night, and during her set she brought out Tame Impala’s Kevin Parker to join her on a pair of tracks.
